{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story23","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_001.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"On our side, we also have valuable resources.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Out of the six books here, we have already@investigated and recorded four of them."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Isabeau's attack"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"was likely due to her sensing a threat from our@actions."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":300,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Sometimes I felt like someone was watching us..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"black","item":[{"path":"resource/scenario/img/51158_tower_tart2/memoria_1733.jpg","posX":0,"posY":0,"visible":"appear"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"blackFrame"},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"surround":"7023_camera"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"bg":"bg_adv_20071.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Huh...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"What's wrong?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_31112.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":810000,"pos":2,"posX":50}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"I also sensed that.@We were probably being watched.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"This \"Ark of Feelings\" is a world within magical@books..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":300}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Isabeau seems to have found a way"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"to interfere with the Ark's workings across time."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"Isabeau is exploiting the wishes of other Magical@Girls for her own purposes."},{"chara":[{"id":810000}],"nameRight":"Qube","textRight":"It's not surprising she can do something like that."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Going out of her way to hinder us"},{"chara":[{"id":402301,"motion":400}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"means that our actions with the \"Ark\" are yielding@results."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"The rebellion La Hire caused was quite extensive."},{"chara":[{"id":402601},{"id":402301,"motion":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Completely quelling it might be difficult..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"But if we can minimize the fires of war,@the world could change significantly."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"There are only two books left in the Ark..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Hence, let's continue"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"recording the memories of La Pucelle with Kagome."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":200,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Kagome & Torte","textCenter":"Yes...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.4,"bg":"bg_adv_31111.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Then...onto the next book.","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"motion":200}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Here we go!"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgm":"stop","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm03_story06","chara":[{"id":102001}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Where are we...?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"It looks like the inside of a castle."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830400,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"","textCenter":"Huh...?"},{"chara":[{"id":830400,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameCenter":"","textBg":"shout","textCenter":"Who are you people?!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830400}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":400,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"[chara:102001:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]...?!"},{"chara":[{"id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Torte","textRight":"Run!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.01,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":402301,"motion":300,"mouthOpen":1}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"Haa...haa...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"chara":[{"id":402601,"motion":300},{"cheek":0,"id":402301,"mouthOpen":0}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"We got carried away and ran,"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"but, I mean, it wouldn't have been suspicious"},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"if we just introduced ourselves properly, right?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Royalty of the Holy Roman Empire...your status is@undoubtedly nobility."},{"chara":[{"id":402301,"motion":1}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"It would be fine if this is an ally's castle,@but if it's not..."},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Let me at least make all of us invisible for now."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Wait, can you do that?"},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":200,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"Yes, with this magic stone..."},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"flashEffect":"flashWhiteSlow2","textClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":402901,"motion":400}],"nameRight":"Perenelle","textRight":"It should keep us from being suspected."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831700,"motion":0,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"[chara:831700:effect_emotion_surprise_0][se:7226_shock]Ah...! This is the Castle of Loches.","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"id":831303}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"You know about it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831700,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"Yeah, it was a long time ago,"},{"chara":[{"id":831700}],"nameRight":"Nicolas","textRight":"but King Charles requested that I bind books for@him."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402901,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"That's something from a while back."},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"Because we were both working as bookbinders,"},{"chara":[{"id":402901}],"nameLeft":"Perenelle","textLeft":"we went all the way to Loches to make the@delivery..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Melissa","textLeft":"I believe it's King Charles's favorite residence,@isn't it?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":1,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameLeft":"Torte","textLeft":"So, this fifth book might be within King Charles's@mind?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":400,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"We'll find out eventually."},{"autoTurnLast":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"turnChangeIn":"rollInFast"},{"chara":[{"id":830200,"lipSynch":0}],"nameCenter":"Charles VII","textCenter":"...","turnChangeOut":"rollOutFast"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830200}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":831303,"motion":100,"pos":1,"soulGem":0}],"nameCenter":"Torte","textCenter":"He's here, King Charles!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":831303,"lipSynch":0,"motion":101,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Torte","textCenter":"[se:7222_happy]..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":831303}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_000.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Charles VII","textCenter":"Haa..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":830200}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":402301,"motion":1,"pos":2},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Melissa","textRight":"He seems alone."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"...This might be our chance![chara:102001:lipSynch_0][wait:1.0][chara:102001:cheek_0][chara:102001:face_mtn_ex_040.exp3.json][chara:102001:lipSynch_1]@But will he listen to us?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":1,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"I will do the talking."},{"chara":[{"id":402601}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"And all of you, show yourselves,@even if it's just as attendants."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":102001,"motion":400,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Kagome","textLeft":"Y-yes...!"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"effect":"fadeout","id":402601},{"effect":"fadeout","id":102001}],"textClear":1},{"autoTurnLast":0.1,"bg":"bg_adv_31094.jpg","bgChangeEffect":"cameraPan"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830200,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"Charles VII","textCenter":"Oh...? Guests, perhaps?"},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"id":830200,"pos":0}],"textClear":1},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":300,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"It's been a while, King Charles."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"Oh! You are from the Holy Roman Empire..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":402601,"motion":1}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"Yes, I am Elisa Celjska of the Order of the Dragon,"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp3.json","id":402601,"motion":100,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"Elisa","textRight":"a friend and ally of La Pucelle."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":830200,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"Charles VII","textLeft":"...La...Pucelle...?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":102001,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300,"pos":2,"soulGem":0}],"nameRight":"Kagome","textRight":"(As I thought...he doesn't remember...)"},{"autoTurnLast":2.0,"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"}]},"version":3}
